Please see GPL or ARTISTIC in docs/ for licensing terms.  You're free to pick
either one as you prefer.  Note that both preserve the rights of the authors
of these programs -- we believe that knowledge should be shared instead of
hoarded and that software should be free.  Consequently, we assert our rights
as the creators and maintainers of this software to prevent anyone from making
this software non-free.

You are welcome to make modifications to this software to suit your needs.  It
would be nice to share those changes with the community.  Please consider
sending patches, extra modules, documentation, or whatever you create.

Thanks!
